data.text:
SV Wildon live scores, players, season schedule and today’s results are available on Sofascore.

SV Wildon next match

SV Wildon will play the next match against LASK Amateure OÖ on Aug 9, 2024, 5:00:00 PM UTC in Regionalliga Mitte.

When the match starts, you will be able to follow LASK Amateure OÖ vs SV Wildon live score, standings, minute by minute updated live results and match statistics.

We may have video highlights with goals and news for some SV Wildon matches, but only if they play their match in one of the most popular football leagues.

SV Wildon previous match

SV Wildon previous match was against Union Gurten in Regionalliga Mitte, the match ended in a draw (1 - 1).

SV Wildon fixtures tab is showing the last 100 football matches with statistics and win/draw/lose icons.

There are also all SV Wildon scheduled matches that they are going to play in the future.

SV Wildon performance and form graph is a Sofascore unique algorithm that we are generating from the team's last 10 matches, statistics, detailed analysis and our own knowledge.

This graph may help predict future SV Wildon matches.
